Alvaro Negredo his bid farewell to Manchester City fans after completing his move to Valencia.

The striker posted an open letter to City fans on Twitter thanking them for all their support for the year he spent at The Etihad.

Negredo, who cost City £20m when he arrived from Sevilla a year ago, began last season with 12 goals in his first 20 appearances but began to struggle and started only three Premier League games after January.

